headline: Electronic Arts (EA) Q2 Earnings Preview: What You Should Know Beyond the Headline Estimates
summary: Get a deeper insight into the potential performance of Electronic Arts (EA) for the quarter ended September 2025 by going beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates and examining the estimates for some of its key metrics.
